sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_resources_owned
FROM resource_owners
WHERE user_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- "top five resources with the most reviews" means selecting the resources with the highest number of evaluations;
- "how many times each has been reviewed" refers to the count of evaluation records for each resource;
- "average score given to each" is the average of the evaluation scores for each resource;
- "different people reviewed each" indicates the count of unique evaluators for each resource.
